#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"FAI rules, allows only FAI start, finish and turn point types, for badges "
"and records. Enables FAI finish height for final glide calculation."
msgstr ""
"Pravila FAI, dozvoljava samo FAI početne, krajnje i tacke okreta za zreci i "
"zreci. Omogućuje FAI krajnju visinu za izračunavanje zavrsnog kliza."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "FAI rules, path from a start to two turn points and return."
msgstr "Pravila FAI, put od početka do dve tacke okreta i povratak."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "FAI rules, path from start to a single turn point and return."
msgstr "Pravila FAI, put od početka do jedne tacke okreta i povratak."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "FAI rules, path from start to a goal destination."
msgstr "Pravila FAI, put od početka do ciljne lokacije."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Racing task around turn points. Can also be used for FAI badge and record "
"tasks. Allows all shapes of observation zones."
msgstr ""
"Racunske zadatak oko tacki okreta. Može se koristiti i za zreci i FAI zreci. "
"Dozvoljava sve forme oblasti observacije."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Task through assigned areas, minimum task time applies. Restricted to "
"cylinder and sector observation zones."
msgstr ""
"Zadatak kroz dodeljene područje, minimumni vreme zadataka primjenjuje se. "
"Ograničen na cilindarske i sektorske oblasti za observaciju."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modified area task. Task with start, finish and at least one predefined 1 "
"mile cylinder. Pilot can add additional points as needed. Minimum task time "
"applies."
msgstr ""
"Modifikovani područni zadatak. Zadatak sa početkom, krajem i barem jednim "
"preddefiniranim cilindrom 1 milja. Pilot može dodati dodatne tacke potrebnim."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Racing task with a mix of assigned areas and turn points, minimum task time "
"applies."
msgstr ""
"Racunske zadatak s kombinacijom dodeljenih podružnica i tacki okreta, "
"minimumni vreme zadataka primjenjuje se."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Casual touring task, uses start and finish cylinders and FAI sector turn "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Složeno putovanje, koristi početne i krajnje cilindre i FAI sektorske tacke "
"okreta."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A 90-degree sector with 1 km radius. Cross corner edge from inside area to "
"start."
msgstr ""
"Sektor 90 stepeni s poluprecnikom od 1 km. Prekorači ivicu iz unutrašnjeg "
"područja do početka."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "A straight line start gate. Cross start gate from inside area to start."
msgstr ""
"Pravilni put za vrata početka. Prekorači vrata iz unutrašnjeg područja do "
"početka."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "A cylinder. Exit area to start."
msgstr "Cilindar. Izađi iz područja do početka."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A 90-degree sector with 'infinite' length sides. Cross any edge, scored from "
"corner point."
msgstr ""
"Sektor 90 stepeni s ivicama 'beskonačne' dužine. Prekorači bilo koju ivicu, "
"ocijenjeno od kotačke točke."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "A keyhole. Scored from center."
msgstr "Ključna otvoraka. Izmereno od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(German rules) Any point within 1/2 km of center or 10 km of a 90-degree "
"sector. Scored from center."
msgstr ""
"(Nemacke pravilnike) Bilo koja točka u poluprecniku 1/2 km okoli centra ali "
"u poluprecniku 10 km okoli sektora s kutom 90 stepeni. Izmereno od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(British rules) Any point within 1/2 km of center or 20 km of a 90-degree "
"sector. Scored from center."
msgstr ""
"(Britanske pravilnike) Bilo koja točka u poluprecniku 1/2 km okoli centra "
"ali u poluprecniku 20 km okoli sektora s kutom 90 stepeni. Izmereno od "
"centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(British rules) Any point within 1/2 km of center or 10 km of a 180-degree "
"sector. Scored from center."
msgstr ""
"(Britanske pravilnike) Bilo koja točka u poluprecniku 1/2 km okoli centra "
"ali u poluprecniku 10 km okoli sektora s kutom 180 stepeni. Izmereno od "
"centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "A cylinder. Any point within area scored from center."
msgstr "Kocka. Bilo koja točka unutar površine izmerena od centra."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "A 1 mile cylinder. Scored by farthest point reached in area."
msgstr "Kocka dužine 1 milja. Izmereno po najdalje doslogi u površini."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "A cylinder. Scored by farthest point reached in area."
msgstr "Kocka. Izmereno po najdalje doslogi u površini."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A sector that can vary in angle and radius. Scored by farthest point reached "
"inside area."
msgstr ""
"Sektor koji se može razlikovati prema kutu i poluprecniku. Izmereno po "
"najdalje doslogi unutar površine."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "A 90-degree sector with 1 km radius. Cross edge to finish."
msgstr ""
"Sektor s kutom 90 stepeni i poluprečnikom 1 km. Prekini granicu za završetak."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cross finish gate line into area to finish."
msgstr "Prekini granicnu liniju za završetak u površinu."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter cylinder to finish."
msgstr "Unesi sektor za završetak."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A 180-degree sector with 5 km radius. Exit area in any direction to start."
msgstr ""
"Sektor s kutom 180 stepeni i poluprečnikom 5 km. Izlazak iz površine u bilo "
"kojem smjeru za početak."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A sector that can vary in angle, inner and outer radius. Scored by farthest "
"point reached inside area."
msgstr ""
"Sektor koji se može razlikovati prema kutu, unutarnjem i vanjskom "
"poluprečniku. Izmereno po najdalje doslogi unutar površine."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "A symmetric quadrant with a custom radius."
msgstr "Simetričan kvadrant s prilagođenim poluprečnikom."

#: src/Task/TypeStrings.cpp:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "A keyhole. Scored by farthest point reached in area."
